CatDescriptText: Portion of related article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 30, 1950, pg. 28, reads: "Kay Boys' Club Scene of Collie Dog Show Sunday.  The community's first professional free dog show will be held in the yard of the Kay Boys Club Sunday, Oct. 1, at 3 P. M.  Arrangements for the event were made with the Collie Club of Western Pennsylvania branch of the Collie Club of America, of which Dr. J. P. McCain is vice president..."
TitMainTitle: J. P. McCain and Mrs. McCain, with two Collie dogs, outside of Kay Boy's Club
